desc: Aqua weed stick is a tool to remove weeds, milfoil and aquatic invasive species from boat trailers, personal watercraft trailers, docks and boat lifts. Push, pull, hook, scrape and cut weeds off with ease using the Aqua Weed Stick.

layout.text: The first and only tool on the market designed to push, pull, hook, scrape and cut weeds off your boat trailer!
PUSH HERE TO NEVER CRAWL UNDER YOUR BOAT AGAIN
